在2015年3月10日为《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》撰写的专栏文章中，威尔士和特雷蒂科夫宣布基金会正在对[[美国国家安全局|美国国家安全局]]和其他五个政府机构和官员，包括[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]提起[[維基媒體基金會控告美國國家安全局案|诉讼]]，质疑其[[大规模监控|大规模监控]]的做法，他们认为这侵犯了基金会读者、编辑和工作人员的宪法权利。加入他们诉讼的还有另外8名原告，包括[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]和[[人权观察|人权观察]]。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Wales|first1=Jimmy|last2=Tretikov|first2=Lila|author-link1=Jimmy Wales|author-link2=Lila Tretikov|title=Stop Spying on Wikipedia Users|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/10/opinion/stop-spying-on-wikipedia-users.html|website=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|access-date=2015-03-10|location=San Francisco|date=2015-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311033930/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/10/opinion/stop-spying-on-wikipedia-users.html|archive-date=2015-03-11|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Paulson|first1=Michelle|last2=Brigham|first2=Geoff|title=Wikimedia v. NSA: Wikimedia Foundation files suit against NSA to challenge upstream mass surveillance|url=https://diff.wikimedia.org/2015/03/10/wikimedia-v-nsa/|website=Wikimedia Diff|access-date=2015-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310140413/https://blog.wikimedia.org/2015/03/10/wikimedia-v-nsa/|archive-date=2015-03-10|url-status=live|date=2015-03-10}}</ref><ref name="rayman">{{cite news |last=Rayman |first=Noah |title=Saving Wikipedia: Meet Lila Tretikov |magazine=[[時代雜誌|Time]] |date=2015-04-14 |url=http://time.com/wikipedia/ |access-date=2015-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418212234/http://time.com/wikipedia/ |archive-date=2015-04-18 |url-status=live }}</ref> 2015年10月23日，[[美国马里兰联邦地区法院|美国马里兰联邦地区法院]]以资格问题为由驳回了'''[[維基媒體基金會控告美國國家安全局案|维基媒体基金会诉国家安全局]]'''的诉讼。美国地区法官{{le|T·S·埃利斯三世|T. S. Ellis III}}裁定，原告无法合理地证明他们受到了{{le|上游监控|upstream surveillance}}，他们的论点“充满了假设”、“猜测”和“数学体操”。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Farivar|first1=Cyrus|date=2015-10-23|title=Judge tosses Wikimedia's anti-NSA lawsuit because Wikipedia isn't big enough. Not enough facts to "plausibly establish that the NSA is using upstream surveillance."|url=https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/10/judge-tosses-wikimedias-anti-nsa-lawsuit-because-wikipedia-isnt-big-enough/|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|access-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120744/http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/10/judge-tosses-wikimedias-anti-nsa-lawsuit-because-wikipedia-isnt-big-enough/|archive-date=2016-03-04|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Wikimedia v. NSA - D. MD. Opinion|url=https://www.aclu.org/legal-document/wikimedia-v-nsa-d-md-opinion|publisher=[[美國公民自由聯盟|ACLU]]|date=2015-10-23|access-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052405/https://www.aclu.org/legal-document/wikimedia-v-nsa-d-md-opinion|archive-date=2016-03-04|url-status=live}}</ref> 原告于2016年2月17日向[[美国联邦第四巡回上诉法院|美国联邦第四巡回上诉法院]]提出上诉。<ref>{{cite web|title=Appeal No. 15-2560. Brief for plaintiffs–appellants|url=https://www.aclu.org/sites/default/files/field_document/23._aclu_appeal_brief_2.17.2016.pdf|publisher=[[美國公民自由聯盟|ACLU]]|date=2016-02-17|access-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312225445/https://www.aclu.org/sites/default/files/field_document/23._aclu_appeal_brief_2.17.2016.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-12|url-status=live}}</ref>

