=== 筹款 ===
在2015年的筹款活动中，一些社群成员表达了他们对筹款横幅的担忧。他们认为，这些横幅对用户来说很碍眼，而且它们可能会欺骗潜在的捐赠者，让人觉得维基百科有直接的财务问题，但事实并非如此。维基媒体基金会发誓要改进进一步筹款活动的措辞以避免这些问题。<ref>{{cite web|first=Caitlin|last=Dewey|title=Wikipedia has a ton of money. So why is it begging you to donate yours?|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2015/12/02/wikipedia-has-a-ton-of-money-so-why-is-it-begging-you-to-donate-yours/|work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|date=2015-12-02|access-date=2018-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710021353/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2015/12/02/wikipedia-has-a-ton-of-money-so-why-is-it-begging-you-to-donate-yours/|archive-date=2018-07-10|url-status=live}}</ref>另外也有人反對基金會接受來自加密貨幣的捐款。2022年4月，维基社区就是否接受加密货币捐款进行投票，结果232人反對加密貨幣捐款，94人支持。<ref>{{cite news |title=维基百科社区投票禁止加密货币捐款 |url=https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=71232 |publisher=solidot}}</ref>2022年5月2日，维基媒体基金会宣布将不再接受加密货币捐款。<ref>{{cite news |title=维基百科运营方决定停止接受加密货币捐款 2022年05月02日 09:06 新浪科技 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2022-05-02/doc-imcwipii7619829.shtml?finpagefr=p_114}}</ref>

=== 解除社群任命的理事职务 ===

2015年6月，[[詹姆斯·海爾曼|詹姆斯·海爾曼]]被社群选举为维基媒体基金会董事会成员。<ref name=board>{{cite web |url=https://diff.wikimedia.org/2015/06/05/board-election-results/ |title=Wikimedia Foundation Board election results are in |work=Wikimedia Diff |date=2015-06-05 |access-date=2015-06-11 |author=Varnum, Gregory |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614011940/https://blog.wikimedia.org/2015/06/05/board-election-results/ |archive-date=2015-06-14 |url-status=live }}</ref> 2015年12月，董事会解除了海尔曼的理事职务，<ref name="removal-resolution">{{cite web |url = https://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Resolution:James_Heilman_Removal |title = Resolution:James Heilman Removal |work = Wikimedia Foundation Board of Trustees |date = 2015-12-28 |access-date = 2015-12-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180215153552/https://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Resolution:James_Heilman_Removal |archive-date = 2018-02-15 |url-status = live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/wikimedia-l/2015-December/080479.html|title=[Wikimedia-l] Announcement about changes to the Board|work=wikimedia.org|access-date=2016-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617160221/https://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/wikimedia-l/2015-December/080479.html|archive-date=2019-06-17|url-status=live}}</ref> 这一决定在维基百科社群的一些成员中引起了争议。<ref name=Lih2016>{{cite news|last1=Lih|first1=Andrew|title=Wikipedia just turned 15 years old. Will it survive 15 more?|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2016/01/15/wikipedia-just-turned-15-years-old-will-it-survive-15-more/|access-date=2016-01-16|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2016-01-15|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225024419/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2016/01/15/wikipedia-just-turned-15-years-old-will-it-survive-15-more/|archive-date=2016-02-25|url-status=live}}</ref> 董事会发表的一份声明宣布，他的同僚对他缺乏信心是他被解职的原因。海尔曼后来表示，他“在过去几周里，'''董事会'''给了他辞职的选择。作为一个社群选举产生的成员，我认为我的任务来自于选举我的社群，因此拒绝这样做。我认为这样做是辜负了那些选举我的人。”<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2016/01/12/wikimedia_dumps_elected_trustee/ | title=Wikimedia Foundation bins community-elected trustee | work=[[The_Register|The Register]] | date=2016-01-12 | access-date=2016-01-27 | author=Orlowski, Andrew | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204024007/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2016/01/12/wikimedia_dumps_elected_trustee/ | archive-date=2016-02-04 | url-status=live }}</ref> 他随后指出，在董事会期间，他曾推动提高维基媒体基金会[[維基百科知識引擎|知识引擎]]项目及其融资的透明度，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rue89.nouvelobs.com/2016/02/26/crise-a-fondation-wikimedia-directrice-demissionne-263290|title=Crise à la fondation Wikimedia : sa directrice démissionne|last=Noisette|first=Thierry|work=[[新觀察家|Nouvel Observateur]]|date=2016-02-26|access-date=2018-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102184156/http://rue89.nouvelobs.com/2016/02/26/crise-a-fondation-wikimedia-directrice-demissionne-263290|archive-date=2016-11-02|url-status=live}}</ref> 并表示他试图公开{{le|骑士基金会|Knight Foundation}}对该引擎的拨款是导致他被解雇的一个因素。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://motherboard.vice.com/read/wikipedias-secret-google-competitor-search-engine-is-tearing-it-apart | title=The Secret Search Engine Tearing Wikipedia Apart | work=Vice | date=2016-02-15 | access-date=2016-02-29 | author=Koebler, Jason | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216072523/http://motherboard.vice.com/read/wikipedias-secret-google-competitor-search-engine-is-tearing-it-apart | archive-date=2016-12-16 | url-status=live }}</ref>

志愿者社群在2017年再次选举海尔曼进入维基媒体基金会董事会。<ref name=Kolbe2017/>

=== 知识引擎 ===

知识引擎是由WMF在2015年发起的一个[[网络搜索引擎|搜索引擎]]项目，目的是在互联网上定位和显示可验证的和值得信赖的信息。<ref name=Koebler2016>{{cite news|url=https://motherboard.vice.com/en_us/article/8q8gvg/wikipedias-secret-google-competitor-search-engine-is-tearing-it-apart|title=The Secret Search Engine Tearing Wikipedia Apart|last=Koebler|first=Jason|date=2016-02-16|work=[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]]|access-date=2018-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709215630/https://motherboard.vice.com/en_us/article/8q8gvg/wikipedias-secret-google-competitor-search-engine-is-tearing-it-apart|archive-date=2018-07-09|url-status=live}}</ref> 知识引擎的目标是减少对传统搜索引擎的依赖，它得到了骑士基金会25万美元的资助。<ref name=McGee2016>{{cite news|url=http://searchengineland.com/wikimedia-foundation-secures-250000-grant-for-search-engine-development-242544|title=Wikimedia Foundation Secures $250,000 Grant For Search Engine Development|last=McGee|first=Matt|date=2016-02-15|work=[[Search_Engine_Land|Search Engine Land]]|access-date=2018-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523004937/http://searchengineland.com/wikimedia-foundation-secures-250000-grant-for-search-engine-development-242544|archive-date=2016-05-23|url-status=live}}</ref> 这个项目被一些人认为是一个丑闻，主要是因为它是在保密的情况下构思的，这被一些人认为是与维基媒体社区的透明度有冲突。事实上，社群可以获得的一些信息是通过《[[The_Signpost|The Signpost]]》在2016年发布的泄露文件得到的。<ref>{{cite web|first=Andreas|last=Kolbe|title=An in-depth look at the newly revealed documents|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Wikipedia_Signpost/2016-02-10/In_focus|work=[[The_Signpost|The Signpost]]|date=2016-02-10|access-date=2018-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901083007/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Wikipedia_Signpost/2016-02-10/In_focus|archive-date=2017-09-01|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=Koebler2016/>在这次争议之后，维基媒体基金会执行主任[[莱拉·特列季科夫|莱拉·特列季科夫]]辞职。<ref>{{cite web|first=Ashley|last=Allen|title=Wikimedia Director Resigns Following Internal Row Over Search Engine Plans|url=https://www.eteknix.com/wikimedia-director-resigns-following-internal-row-search-engine-plans/|work=eteknix|access-date=2018-07-09|date=2016-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710010458/https://www.eteknix.com/wikimedia-director-resigns-following-internal-row-search-engine-plans/|archive-date=2018-07-10|url-status=live}}</ref>

=== 財政度支出 ===
